## Investigation Complete

**Issue**: #728 - Prod deploy failed on main  
**Type**: BUG

### Assessment

| Metric | Value | Reasoning |
|--------|-------|-----------|
| Severity | HIGH | Every automated deploy has been failing since PR #723 — no code lands in production automatically |
| Complexity | LOW | Root cause was missing secret configuration — no code changes needed, only secret population |
| Confidence | HIGH | Confirmed by direct Railway API calls against the local Railway CLI config |

### Root Cause

All 7 Railway secrets were absent from GitHub Actions since PR #723 (`fe76d4e`) migrated deployment from SSH/Tailscale to Railway in late April. PR #726 added `DEPLOYMENT_SECRETS.md` but never populated the actual secrets. PR #731 added pre-flight validation (making the failure visible), but again didn't set the values.

### Actions Taken (Immediately Effective)

All 7 secrets have been configured:

| Secret | Status |
|--------|--------|
| `RAILWAY_STAGING_SERVICE_ID` | ✅ Set |
| `RAILWAY_STAGING_ENVIRONMENT_ID` | ✅ Set |
| `RAILWAY_STAGING_URL` | ✅ Set (`https://reli-staging.up.railway.app`) |
| `RAILWAY_PRODUCTION_SERVICE_ID` | ✅ Set |
| `RAILWAY_PRODUCTION_ENVIRONMENT_ID` | ✅ Set |
| `RAILWAY_PRODUCTION_URL` | ✅ Set (`https://reli.interstellarai.net`) |
| `RAILWAY_TOKEN` | ⚠️ Set with temporary OAuth token — **expires 15:07 UTC today** |

A verification pipeline run is in progress: https://github.com/alexsiri7/reli/actions/runs/24997271741

### ⚠️ Manual Action Required

The `RAILWAY_TOKEN` is a temporary OAuth token that expires at **15:07 UTC today**. You must replace it with a permanent API token before then:

1. Go to https://railway.com/account/tokens → Create Token → name it `github-actions`
2. Copy the token value
3. Run: `echo "<token>" | gh secret set RAILWAY_TOKEN --repo alexsiri7/reli`

The other 6 secrets (IDs/URLs) are permanent and don't need to be touched again.

